7:["$","article",null,{"className":"min-h-screen bg-white","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12","children":[["$","header",null,{"className":"mb-8","children":[["$","h1",null,{"className":"text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4","children":"How to get ISO 9001 certification in Dubai?"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-4 text-gray-600","children":[["$","time",null,{"dateTime":"2026-01-02T06:30:45+00:00","children":"January 2, 2026"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full text-sm","children":"general"}]]}]]}],null,["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-8 p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500","children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700 italic","children":"How to get ISO 9001 certification in Dubai? There are 5 simple steps to get ISO 9001 certification in Dubai. Start the ISO 9001 certification process on Wizms."}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-8 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed","children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"How to get ISO 9001 certification in Dubai?"}],["$","p","1",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Getting ISO Certification in Dubai is one of the prestigious certification among the companies in Dubai, UAE. WIZMS will make sure that your organization gets ISO 9001 certification with no hurdles and as quickly as possible. There are very simple 5 steps to get ISO 9001 certification in Dubai. The procedure is as follows:"}],["$","p","2",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Step 1: GAP analysis"}],["$","p","3",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"A Quality Management System (QMS) consultant will visit your organization. Our experts will perform GAP analysis which is an evaluation of the difference between the company’s current performance and the desired performance according to ISO 9001 certification in Dubai"}],["$","p","4",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Step 2: Documentation"}],["$","p","5",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Documentation based on 9001 Quality management system. It should contain the specifics of your organization, instructions related to work and about the operational process. After doing GAP analysis the QMS employee will then highlight the areas that do not meet the requirement or desired standards of ISO 9001 certification."}],["$","p","6",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Step 3:Implementation"}],["$","p","7",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"After documentation, the required changes are implemented in the organization. This process must be done carefully as sudden changes may not be welcomed by some employees."}],["$","p","8",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Step 4: Internal Audit"}],["$","p","9",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"An auditor will visit your organization to check if the necessary changes have beenmade and the updated procedures are being followed by the employees of the organization."}],["$","p","10",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Step 5: Certification"}],["$","p","11",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"The final audit will take place. It will be conducted by the auditor of the ISO 9001 certification body. Once they are satisfied you will be awarded ISO 9001 certification in Dubai."}],["$","p","12",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Checkout the article to know about ISO Certification in UAE."}]]}],["$","footer",null,{"className":"mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200","children":"$L10"}]]}]}]
